308337665.name: XY—Fates Collide
308337665.description: Mega Alakazam-EX sees the future—and shapes it to unify two worlds! The Legendary Pokémon Zygarde arrives in many different Formes to bring order, together with Lugia BREAK, Mega Altaria-EX, and Umbreon-EX. Fates are sealed, and two Pokémon worlds join together in the Pokémon TCG: XY—Fates Collide expansion!

308337667.name: XY—Fates Collide Evolution Pack

BattleRulerBundle.name: Battle Ruler
BattleRulerBundle.description: Rule the battle with the Legendary Pokémon of order and control: Zygarde! With Lucario's fists of justice and Serperior's crushing coils, you'll bring order to chaos and seize the moment with the Battle Ruler theme deck. On to victory!

BattleRulerPCD.name: Battle Ruler
BattleRulerPCD.description: Rule the battle with the Legendary Pokémon of order and control: Zygarde! With Lucario's fists of justice and Serperior's crushing coils, you'll bring order to chaos and seize the moment with the Battle Ruler theme deck. On to victory!

MegaMawileBox.name: Mega Mawile-EX Premium Collection
MegaMawileBox.description:
Beware the devious Mawile, a sweet-looking Pokémon with powerful steel jaws—and Mega Mawile-EX has even more chomping power! Get the Mega Mawile-EX Premium Collection, and add the Deceiver Pokémon to your next game!

The Pokémon TCG: Mega Mawile-EX Premium Collection includes:

• 1 never-before-seen foil promo card featuring Mega Mawile-EX
• 1 never-before-seen foil promo card featuring Mawile-EX
• 1 Mawile Spirit Link card to get this Mega Evolution Pokémon into play fast
• 6 Pokémon TCG booster packs to mega-expand your collection
• 1 cool new Mega Mawile coin

SkyGuardianBundle.name: Sky Guardian
SkyGuardianBundle.description: Unleash a storm of battle with the Legendary Pokémon of the seas: Lugia! With the fiery wings of Moltres and the mystic flame of Delphox, you'll burn through opposition in a flash with the Sky Guardian theme deck. Light it up!

SkyGuardianPCD.name: Sky Guardian
SkyGuardianPCD.description: Unleash a storm of battle with the Legendary Pokémon of the seas: Lugia! With the fiery wings of Moltres and the mystic flame of Delphox, you'll burn through opposition in a flash with the Sky Guardian theme deck. Light it up!

XY10EliteTrainerBox.name: XY—Fates Collide Elite Trainer Box: Mega Alakazam
XY10EliteTrainerBox.description:
Reality Shifts—and Is Remade!

Mega Alakazam-EX sees the future—and shapes it to unify two worlds! The Legendary Pokémon Zygarde arrives in many different Formes to bring order, together with Lugia BREAK, Mega Altaria-EX, and Umbreon-EX. Fates are sealed, and two Pokémon worlds join together in the Pokémon TCG: XY—Fates Collide expansion!

Join the Elite Trainers with the TCG: XY—Fates Collide Elite Trainer Box! Inside, you'll find:
• 8 Pokémon TCG: XY—Fates Collide booster packs
• 65 card sleeves featuring Mega Alakazam
• 45 Pokémon TCG Energy cards
• A player's guide to the XY—Fates Collide expansion
• 6 damage-counter dice
• 1 competition-legal coin-flip die
• 2 acrylic condition markers
• A collector's box to hold everything, with 4 dividers to keep it organized
• A code card for the Pokémon Trading Card Game Online

XerneasEXSummerTin2016.name: Rainbow Team
XerneasEXSummerTin2016.description: With Xerneas-EX leading the charge, you can use the Sky Field Stadium card to keep even more Pokémon types in play and hit hard with Rainbow Force. It's a team effort!

YveltalEXSummerTin2016.name: Night Prowl
YveltalEXSummerTin2016.description: Yveltal-EX is brewing up a victory, using Max Elixir to fuel its Evil Ball attack for big damage. Draw lots of cards to turn Noctowl's High Flight into a power attack! Time to prowl!

ZygardeEXSummerTin2016.name: Power Arsenal
ZygardeEXSummerTin2016.description: With lots of Stadium cards, Zygarde-EX can dish out quick damage, while Trainer cards and Mamoswine's Ability reduce your opponent's damage to a trickle. Stay strong!
